===Etymology 1===
[[Image:Accetta.jpg|thumb|right|An axe]]
From {{etyl|enm|en}}, from {{etyl|ang|en}} {{m|ang|æx}}, from {{etyl|gem-pro|en}} {{m|gem-pro|*akwisī}}, probably from a {{etyl|ine-pro|en}} {{m|ine-pro|*h₂egʷs-ih₂-||axe}}, from {{m|ine-pro|*h₂eḱ-||sharp, pointed}}. Compare {{etyl|de|-}} {{m|de|Axt}}, {{etyl|da|-}} {{m|da|økse}}, {{etyl|is|-}} {{m|is|öxi}}, and also {{etyl|la|-}} {{m|la|ascia}}.

